Will this be a breaking change? You've added a new parameter to this public method in the Android platform. Will calls such as ImageUtils.resize(bitmap, 100, 100) continue to work?
You can mitigate this by adding the following method:
  public static Bitmap resize(Bitmap bitmap, final int width, final int height) {
    resize(bitmap, width, height, false);
  }

